channel.title: [667] Other teleport
channel.description:
Hello guys, On my 718 RSPS I have a box that teleports you home (If you do ;;home you get in the box and boom you are home) But I don't know if it's possible on a 667 RSPS, Does any one knows and can you tell me how it works? Thank you!
- Oblivion
